{"tid":1313084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Now新聞台] 商店老闆自費向遊行人士派水，他認為水貨客較遊行的影響更大。","createTime":"2019-07-13T16:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:34:34.000Z","uid":10200,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"364562ebcfe3dc30a3e8521984c2079d22098367","tid":1313084,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】至於較早前的光復上水遊行，有居民指水貨客嚴重影響生活，有商店老闆指水貨客推高租金，影響區內民生，要求當局嚴正執法，主辦單位指有三萬人參加。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍按原定時間約下午三時半從北區運動場出發，遊行以「光復上水」為主題，希望政府執法，減輕水貨客對上水居民的滋擾。<br />\n<br />\n除了水貨客，亦有人希望政府繼續回應撤回修例等的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n有連鎖店拉閘，有職員和顧客在內等候；有商店老闆自費向遊行人士派水，他認為水貨客較遊行的影響更大。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有內地旅客因為遊行影響行程，她表示不理解遊行人士的行動。<br />\n<br />\n遊行期間，有蒙面的男子在商店的閉路電視貼上貼紙遮蓋。有遊行人士在街柱和路牌上以便利貼表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n隊頭約一個多小時抵達終點上水花園，遊行人士之後陸續散去。遊行發起人梁金成認為，即使藥房關門，也不影響遊行的成效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355284&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355284%26refer%3DShare&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=c99fb866\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355284%26refer%3DShare&h=68818bc9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355284&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無線新聞食撚屎 袁志偉落地獄</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f831356708e9d1d95ca3a6fb38ac783ff906414b","tid":1313084,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T16:29:09.000Z","